Class MultipartEntityWithProgressListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.http.entity.mime.MultipartEntity
      • com.box.boxjavalibv2.httpentities.MultipartEntityWithProgressListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.http.HttpEntity

    public class MultipartEntityWithProgressListener
extends org.apache.http.entity.mime.MultipartEntity
    This is a class wrappying MultipartEntity with a IFIleTransferListener so the writing progress of the entity can be monitored.
